** Recovery from Peer Isolation

  $ java TestRunner {{{./java/freepastry/TestPeerIsolation.java}freepastry.test.TestPeerIsolation}}

  $ java TestRunner {{{./java/openchord/TestPeerIsolation.java}openchord.test.TestPeerIsolation}}

